            <dt class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1E1B4B]">Is Math Practice free to use?</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#6B7280] leading-relaxed">Yes, completely free. No account, no subscription, and no ads. Every practice mode on the site is available to anyone.</dd>
          </div>
