            <dt class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1E1B4B]">Do I need to create an account or log in?</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#6B7280] leading-relaxed">No. Practice starts the moment you arrive. There's no signup, no login, and no personal data collected.</dd>
